data.description: This almost 70 acres of beautiful woodland is an outdoor lover's paradise! This custom built home boasts over 4800 ft.² almost 2000 of which is a beautiful finished basement with a kitchen, full bathroom, and separate entrance. A large sunroom, custom maple cabinets and doors throughout, new flooring, a beautiful new custom stone wood-burning fireplace and many other upgrades are just a few of the interior features you will see at 190 Orchard Rd. This property is full of mature timbers, a large pond, multiple outbuildings and barn, fully fenced, and all of the mineral rights and appliances convey! With the property boundary near Woolly Hollow State Park, this property is perfect for the farmer, hunter, fisherman, or outdoor lover who needs lots of space: both inside and out. This is the dream! Reach out today to schedule your personal property tour!
